{"tid":268207,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港天文台：6月4日多雲，有驟雨及幾陣雷暴。","createTime":"2017-06-03T00:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T03:07:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d5c0f36daac752424a6ecf6ab4ceb1fcecb36ab","tid":268207,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T00:27:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/fndc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fcurrwx%2Ffndc.htm&d=oDXEYGnpFcyUeXg9UHvZKEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=9b6be4fc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/fndc.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n天氣概況:<br />\n一 道 低 壓 槽 會 在 今 明 兩 天 為 華 南 帶 來 驟 雨 及 雷 暴 。 預 料 該 低 壓 槽 會 在 下 週 初 逐 漸 減 弱 。 而 隨 著 西 北 太 平 洋 的 高 壓 脊 向 西 伸 展 ， 下 週 中 期 中 國 東 南 部 漸 轉 天 晴 炎 熱 。<br />\n<br />\n6月4日 (日)<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/images/wxicon/pic63.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fimages%2Fwxicon%2Fpic63.png&h=8b95ed79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多 雲 ， 有 驟 雨 及 幾 陣 雷 暴 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/ws/304/amz/worldservice/live/assets/images/2013/06/04/130604132828_hk-64-martin.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fws%2F304%2Famz%2Fworldservice%2Flive%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F2013%2F06%2F04%2F130604132828_hk-64-martin.gif&h=bc25434e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07d574a06f1db98031d4f9eae3e554d0acae9139","tid":268207,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T00:33:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">料全日驟雨兼雷暴 初時雨勢頗大</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170603/56776218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170603%2F56776218&d=oDXEYGnpFcyUeXg9UHvZKEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=780d6a57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170603%2F56776218&h=ad51222a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170603/56776218</a><br />\n<br />\n天文台指，一道低壓槽將為本港帶來驟雨及雷暴，其中六四當日，預計「初時（中午前）雨勢有時頗大」，下周一仍有驟雨，「初時有幾陣雷暴，稍後雨勢減弱」。<br />\n<br />\n天文台又指，該低壓槽下周初會逐漸減弱，而隨着西北太平洋的高壓脊向西伸展，下周中起本港將連日天晴炎熱，市區最高氣溫至少一連5日升至32&deg;C。"},{"pid":"04ac04d8ea61765064de2ca7efafcac75dd0c8ae","tid":268207,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T00:55:20.000Z","msg":"出面勁好天 wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7c308d5fa1c5668841853c4cf54e5ee89c57fd","tid":268207,"uid":11464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T00:55:42.000Z","msg":"五雷轟頂"},{"pid":"8b30c56cbae0efdb58f5db2c0a1c1632fb6107cd","tid":268207,"uid":3659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T00:58:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">六四夜邪壇雷電再</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe81affb5a283c009d13e75e3608841f7f0c610","tid":268207,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T02:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出面勁好天 wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你係未來回post?"},{"pid":"73433275e951d92eaea5bcc7c5fa9f7e12db404f","tid":268207,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T03:07:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出面勁好天 wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你係未來回post?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}